OL,6,FA mother from Wigan, who has spent
OL,7,Fmore than a decade trying to find a
OL,8,Fcure for her son, and thousands like
OL,9,Fhim, has been honoured at Windsor
OL,10,FCastle.
OL,12,FAlex Johnson founded the charity
OL,13,F'Joining Jack' 12 years ago after her
OL,14,Fson, Jack, was diagnosed with the
OL,15,Fmuscle-wasting disease .
OL,17,FAfter raising more than #2 million for
OL,18,Fthe charity, she received an Order of
OL,19,Fthe British Empire (OBE) from the
OL,20,FPrincess Royal on Wednesday January 24.
