OL,6,FJack was 3-years-old when he was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with Duchenne Muscular
OL,8,FDystrophy.
OL,10,FIt is a disease which affects 1 in
OL,11,Fevery 3,500 boys worldwide.
OL,13,FThere is still no cure, but thanks to
OL,14,FAlex and husband, former , Andy
OL,15,FJohnson, it's getting closer.
OL,17,FWith support from the world of sport
OL,18,Fand showbusiness - and a well-known
OL,19,Flink-fingered salute - the Joining
OL,20,FJack charity has raised more than #2
OL,21,Fmillion for research.
