OL,3,CMum given OBE for work trying to find
OL,4,Ca cure for her son
OL,6,FIt's paid for doctors, nurses and new
OL,7,Fdrugs, drugs which are slowing down
OL,8,Fthe progression of the disease.
OL,10,FAlex told ITV News, "I feel really
OL,11,Fprivileged because it was given to me
OL,12,Fbut it's for my family, for Jack, for
OL,13,FJames, for Andy, for all of my
OL,14,Ffriends, for everybody who supported
OL,15,Fus since Jack was diagnosed, it really
OL,16,Fis for them.
