OL,3,CMum given OBE for work trying to find
OL,4,Ca cure for her son
OL,6,F"It represents how far we've come in
OL,7,Fthe past 10 years, from us getting
OL,8,FJack's diagnosis and being told to go
OL,9,Faway basically and give him the best
OL,10,Flife we can, to us last month managing
OL,11,Fto get the first treatment for
OL,12,FDuchenne approved by the regulator in
OL,13,Fthe UK.
OL,15,F"So I think it shows the work that has
OL,16,Fhappened and how the landscape for the
OL,17,FDuchenne community has changed."
