OL,6,FSince his diagnosis, Jack has lost
OL,7,Fstrength in his legs and his father
OL,8,Fsays he is moving into a wheelchair
OL,9,Fmore full time.
OL,11,FEventually, Jack may need spinal rods
OL,12,Fto keep him upright and ventilation to
OL,13,Fhelp him breathe.
OL,15,FJack's story has inspired the nation,
OL,16,Fwith celebrities donning the "linked-
OL,17,Ffingers salute".
OL,19,FAlex says their fight for a cure for
OL,20,Fthe disease continues.
